data.description: THIS IS THE ONE! Arguably the best corner lot in the highly desired Lantern Walk is finally here! This FULLY RENOVATED 3/2 home boasts tons of natural light, brand new LVP floors, updated bathrooms, accent walls w/ designer wainscoting, chef's kitchen w/ SS appliances & breakfast nook w/ built-in island, spacious 1 car garage w/ epoxy floor, front & rear screened in patios, vaulted ceilings, & so much more! You'll enjoy peace of mind having storm protecting accordion shutters throughout. The LOW HOA payments cover roof maintenance & repairs, & HOA just completed exterior painting & new gutters (2024) w/ NO ASSESSMENTS and great reserves! Close to major highways, airports, shopping & beaches, you can enjoy all South FL has to offer! Act fast to schedule a tour & embrace the FL lifestyle.
